cast.overview: Singer Freddie Mercury, guitarist Brian May, drummer Roger Taylor and bass guitarist John Deacon take the music world by storm when they form the rock 'n' roll band Queen in 1970. Hit songs become instant classics. When Mercury's increasingly wild lifestyle starts to spiral out of control, Queen soon faces its greatest challenge yet – finding a way to keep the band together amid the success and excess.
cast.title: Bohemian Rhapsody

cast.overview: The beloved Crawleys and their intrepid staff prepare for the most important moment of their lives. A royal visit from the King and Queen of England will unleash scandal, romance and intrigue that will leave the future of Downton hanging in the balance.
cast.title: Downton Abbey

details.biography: Jonathan Cheetham was born on 26 February 1982 in Sheffield, Yorkshire, England, UK. He is an actor, known for The War of the Worlds (2019), Downton Abbey (2019) and Bohemian Rhapsody (2018).
details.name: Jonathan Cheetham
